03:35.440 --> 03:37.400
Sounds exactly
like St Eligius.

03:37.400 --> 03:39.800
The Chief of Services
has cancer.

03:39.800 --> 03:43.640
The Director of Medicine is seeing
this knockout first-year resident.

03:43.640 --> 03:46.480
Listen. "She fell lymph
into my arms."

03:46.480 --> 03:50.480
Let me see that.

03:51.120 --> 03:52.240
Doe!

