under your wing and pull some out..

05:39.000 --> 05:41.320
I'd laugh, but
my gizzard's killing me.

05:41.320 --> 05:44.400
Well, let me
take a gander.

05:44.400 --> 05:46.760
Anytime I eat anything
stronger than milk,

05:46.760 --> 05:48.720
