burning pain here.

05:48.720 --> 05:50.440
Taking aspirin?

05:50.440 --> 05:51.880
No.  Arthritis medicine?

05:51.880 --> 05:53.040
No.

05:53.040 --> 05:55.200
You ever had an ulcer?

05:55.200 --> 05:56.680
Not me, but Dad did.

05:56.680 --> 06:00.680
OK, I'm going to order
a GI series for you.

06:00.720 --> 06:04.360
Well, now I've got something
to look forward to(!)

06:04.360 --> 06:05.800
I'd better call Dippy.

06:05.800 --> 06:08.680
cos when I get behind
in deliveries,

06:08.680 --> 06:12.680
