06:31.280 --> 06:34.880
DOOR OPENS

06:34.880 --> 06:36.880
What do you think?

06:36.880 --> 06:40.520
You're too late for Halloween.
Been rummaging around in your attic?

06:40.520 --> 06:42.160
One of my
favourite chapeaux.

06:42.160 --> 06:43.680
1941.

06:43.680 --> 06:45.800
A stylish brim.

06:45.800 --> 06:47.840
I favour the MacArthur
tilt myself.

06:47.840 --> 06:50.880
The general always
affects a jaunty rake.

06:50.880 --> 06:54.160
Can't you see
I'm reading?

06:54.160 --> 06:55.240
Ah, the Cutting Edge.

06:55.240 --> 06:58.040
Katharine just borrowed that book
from the Havenhursts.

06:58.040 --> 06:59.760
It's nestled now
on my nightstand.

06:59.760 --> 07:01.200
What do you think?

07:01.200 --> 07:05.200
