Board of Trustees meeting.

07:14.400 --> 07:16.120
It's imperative
you attend.

07:16.120 --> 07:18.280
We need another
strong voice

07:18.280 --> 07:20.600
to shut down
the sycophants.

07:20.600 --> 07:23.480
The board commissioned
an independent feasibility study,

07:23.480 --> 07:24.560
and I got a sneak peek.

07:24.560 --> 07:27.480
I smell trouble.

07:27.480 --> 07:30.040
These mints are useless.
What time?

07:30.040 --> 07:32.040
Tomorrow, six o'clock.

07:32.040 --> 07:34.000
See you later,
alligator.

07:34.000 --> 07:37.280
Well, come on now, it's your turn.
In a while...

07:37.280 --> 07:39.000
Will you get out of here?

07:39.000 --> 07:43.000
