with that kind of spirit.

07:44.680 --> 07:46.720
"Tulips on the organ."

07:46.720 --> 07:48.600
My words.

07:48.600 --> 07:49.920
My book!

07:49.920 --> 07:51.400
Doe stole my book.

07:51.400 --> 07:53.160
I'll kill him.

07:53.160 --> 07:57.160
SMASHING

