09:47.880 --> 09:48.880
Yeah?

09:48.880 --> 09:50.760
Yeah?

09:50.760 --> 09:52.200
In private?

09:52.200 --> 09:56.080
Sure. Come on.

09:56.080 --> 10:00.080
Go ahead, Fiscus.
I'm listening.

10:01.320 --> 10:04.360
Well, sir...

10:04.360 --> 10:06.280
this is kind of
complicated.

10:06.280 --> 10:08.960
It's about doctor-patient
confidentiality.

10:08.960 --> 10:10.160
Ah.

10:10.160 --> 10:14.160
Should we be having
this conversation?

10:16.680 --> 10:20.480
I've got a patient, who I'll call
"A," with complications,

10:20.480 --> 10:23.880
and also a relationship with a
member of this patient's family,

10:23.880 --> 10:25.280
who I'll call "B".

10:25.280 --> 10:28.320
