to know what I know about "A."

10:28.320 --> 10:30.720
Now, does your patient want the
family member to know?

10:30.720 --> 10:32.680
Now, does your patient want the
family member to know?

10:32.680 --> 10:35.000
I think your job is to convince "A"
to tell "B".

10:35.000 --> 10:36.320
I tried.

10:36.320 --> 10:38.440
I think that "B"
would be angry at me

10:38.440 --> 10:40.680
for withholding the information.

10:40.680 --> 10:42.440
Ah, well, that puts
you up against

10:42.440 --> 10:44.800
the classic ethical
question, doesn't it?

10:44.800 --> 10:47.320
In other words, you can
do right by "B",

10:47.320 --> 10:50.720
but then you risk
losing "A's" trust.

10:50.720 --> 10:52.000
I see.

10:52.000 --> 10:54.440
Well, thank you
for your help.

10:54.440 --> 10:57.280
Is there something you're not
telling me about this case?

10:57.280 --> 10:58.920
Your daughter Lizzie?

10:58.920 --> 11:00.600
What about her?

11:00.600 --> 11:04.600
She's pregnant.

11:13.320 --> 11:16.200
