a patient, Dr Bedder.

11:21.200 --> 11:23.400
Whose viscera are
you vivisecting?

11:23.400 --> 11:24.440
Bill Belvedere.

11:24.440 --> 11:28.400
Belvedere. Right. Massive MI
arrived COD a couple hours ago.

11:28.400 --> 11:30.840
So what tray's he on?
I need to get started.

11:30.840 --> 11:31.920
Can this wait?

11:31.920 --> 11:34.640
I'm swamped right now.
People dying who haven't before.

11:34.640 --> 11:37.080
Don't worry,
I'll stay out of your way.

11:37.080 --> 11:39.440
What's the point?
I see this all the time.

11:39.440 --> 11:41.000
The guy had a faulty clock,

11:41.000 --> 11:44.480
stuffs himself with
guacamole and chips,

