12:59.000 --> 13:02.040
Hello, dear.

13:02.040 --> 13:06.040
Dr Arrowsmith. Just visited a
patient of mine, Debbie Hoffman.

13:06.120 --> 13:08.000
Are you on staff here?

13:08.000 --> 13:09.440
God forbid, no.

13:09.440 --> 13:11.280
I'm her family's private
physician.

13:11.280 --> 13:14.240
I'm looking for the young man
who admitted and treated her -

13:14.240 --> 13:15.800
Dr Chandler.

13:15.800 --> 13:17.760
Last time I saw him,

13:17.760 --> 13:19.680
he was headed
toward on-call.

13:19.680 --> 13:22.560
May I ask you
a personal question?

13:22.560 --> 13:24.080
Where did you get
that lovely sweater?

13:24.080 --> 13:26.880
Where did you get
that lovely sweater?

13:26.880 --> 13:28.800
Maybe I'll
surprise my wife.

13:28.800 --> 13:31.360
I rarely get to this section of
town. Thank you, dear.

13:31.360 --> 13:33.480
Rosenthal. Nurse Rosenthal.

13:33.480 --> 13:37.480
On-call, huh?

13:42.680 --> 13:44.120
Excuse me.

13:44.120 --> 13:45.400
Yeah?

13:45.400 --> 13:47.160
Dr Chandler?

13:47.160 --> 13:48.840
Mm-hmm.

13:48.840 --> 13:50.560
Dr Arrowsmith.

13:50.560 --> 13:52.760
I'm the Johnson
family physician.

13:52.760 --> 13:54.200
So?

13:54.200 --> 13:57.080
You're treating the granddaughter,
Debbie Hoffman.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.520
Yeah. Yeah. That's right.

13:58.520 --> 14:01.320
Well, at her mother's request,
I took a peek.

14:01.320 --> 14:04.280
And, frankly, I'm alarmed
at your treatment,

14:04.280 --> 14:05.800
which seems
casual at best.

14:05.800 --> 14:08.040
According to the latest
journal reports,

14:08.040 --> 14:12.000
most ulcers can be successfully
treated with cimetidine.

14:12.000 --> 14:14.120
A mailbox full of glossy
subscriptions

14:14.120 --> 14:16.280
doesn't make up for
years of experience.

14:16.280 --> 14:19.080
Perhaps you don't know
everything about this case.

14:19.080 --> 14:20.320
Look, Dr Arrowsmith,

14:20.320 --> 14:23.680
I understand you used to put
patients on restricted diets,

14:23.680 --> 14:25.600
magnesia-alumina suspension,

14:25.600 --> 14:29.200
but time has proven most of these
remedies make people worse.

14:29.200 --> 14:31.120
You must be a first-year intern.

14:31.120 --> 14:34.000
Overeager to use
the latest procedure.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.440
Impress higher-ups.

14:35.440 --> 14:39.040
I'm in my third year and frankly
I've seen a lot of you old guys

14:39.040 --> 14:41.800
with your private practices
sitting on your behind

14:41.800 --> 14:43.840
in the 'burbs,
getting soft and lazy

14:43.840 --> 14:46.440
on out-of-date information
and techniques,

14:46.440 --> 14:48.840
giving the rest of us
a bad name.

14:48.840 --> 14:51.160
Who's your supervisor?

14:51.160 --> 14:54.560
(SIGHS) If you'll excuse me,
I got to get some sleep.

14:54.560 --> 14:58.560
I've been on duty
for 36 hours.

15:03.120 --> 15:07.120
You work fast. Mr Belvedere
couldn't even have been cold yet.

15:07.240 --> 15:09.280
The race is
to the swift.

15:09.280 --> 15:11.440
Time, essence,
freshness.

15:11.440 --> 15:14.200
The market
is very particular,

15:14.200 --> 15:15.720
and the margins
are thin.

15:15.720 --> 15:16.840
Just heads?

15:16.840 --> 15:18.400
Oh, no. An assortment.

15:18.400 --> 15:20.280
Arms, feet, organs.

15:20.280 --> 15:21.400
For transplant?

15:21.400 --> 15:23.360
We now have
the technology,

15:23.360 --> 15:25.440
so a whole black market
is springing up.

15:25.440 --> 15:28.200
Where do you
sell these...parts?

15:28.200 --> 15:30.080
Research facilities,
med schools.

15:30.080 --> 15:33.320
The lesser-known places
have trouble getting enough bodies.

15:33.320 --> 15:36.520
Do you know how many medical students
there are now?

15:36.520 --> 15:39.720
The numbers are staggering. They need
corpses to practise on.

15:39.720 --> 15:41.560
Nothing wrong
with what I'm doing.

15:41.560 --> 15:42.960
Bull!

15:42.960 --> 15:46.320
Who's to know? They're dead.
They don't need them.

15:46.320 --> 15:50.320
Besides, I normally use indigents,
people with no families.

15:52.800 --> 15:55.040
I made a mistake
this time.

15:55.040 --> 15:56.960
I want
Mr Belvedere's head

15:56.960 --> 15:59.880
returned to his body
right now.

15:59.880 --> 16:00.880
You're not going to blow
the whistle, are you?

